{"tid":467800,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"東廊東行北角入隧支路需唔需要劃一條做巴士專線","createTime":"2017-11-13T23:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T05:04:44.000Z","uid":108894,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"64efeeb40ceced8d50e7ee66101ccbc784f793fc","tid":467800,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T23:36:57.000Z","msg":"呢幾年東廊東行北角入東隧真係塞到飛起<br />\n成日係塞到唔行果隻<br />\n而家搭307/603/681果D線放工真係好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔塞車大約40-45分鐘就可以由興發街番到自己區頭站，比個東廓入口搞一搞即刻多半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (307/681仲要有大老山慢車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n如果東廊北角果邊其中一線劃做巴士專線應該可以好少少<br />\n其他車一係你就慢慢塞，一係就行紅隧西隧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b539920cb2f21e5c5a2607b713f87c92de5eac1","tid":467800,"uid":12338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T23:42:30.000Z","msg":"倒塞返銅鑼灣咪冚家剷囉柒頭<br />\n仲想快？"},{"pid":"ae522cc8d7466be53ee87425f7666fa1ca68421d","tid":467800,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:36:37.000Z","msg":"你老味閪而家興發街搭307<br />\n6點鐘上車冇7:20都入唔到大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點都搞搞佢好wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3cc5cc8c70c5a5709c765898e7d9501c5f56e8","tid":467800,"uid":28258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老味閪而家興發街搭307<br />\n6點鐘上車冇7:20都入唔到大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點都搞搞佢好wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收工時間邊到都塞<br />\n有咩法子呢?<br />\n倒不如叫僱主制定返流動返\u001b放工時間仲好啦"},{"pid":"0475898e3ee90fbe06470141b27b2f5b80e7978c","tid":467800,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T01:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你老味閪而家興發街搭307<br />\n6點鐘上車冇7:20都入唔到大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點都搞搞佢好wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收工時間邊到都塞<br />\n有咩法子呢?<br />\n倒不如叫僱主制定返流動返\u001b放工時間仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n搭紅隧巴有巴士專線，順D嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ec19b12d168df64c8a893cba222116af1f02a7","tid":467800,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T02:21:38.000Z","msg":"其實307行紅隧可能仲快"},{"pid":"ab1b9abc2986e3238238d8645a72a8455af56a41","tid":467800,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T02:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實307行紅隧可能仲快</blockquote><br />\n早年307開大埔回程就係行紅隧<br />\n到02年先改東隧"},{"pid":"7a6de7af08c75ddb06bb8ae4e75bbfb1fdab94f5","tid":467800,"uid":10206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"我搭開307最塞反而係灣仔果段"},{"pid":"4b5dd4aabb1e6251182a96d17cd620d920f3fe63","tid":467800,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T02:38:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我搭開307最塞反而係灣仔果段</blockquote><br />\n入境處果度都塞，但係短嘛<br />\n東隧果度由北角開始就停晒係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c27aaef33d14e29ce44f9067ee889de14474dd","tid":467800,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T02:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實307行紅隧可能仲快</blockquote><br />\n早年307開大埔回程就係行紅隧<br />\n到02年先改東隧</blockquote><br />\n早年307得幾班添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剛剛開果時無咩人坐，果時仲要係城巴果d絨椅，好吉好唔舒服"},{"pid":"de6ec740644073b56b37b56e61f021e5eedefd07","tid":467800,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T02:44:18.000Z","msg":"不過東隧條龍消化得好快，因為西行入東隧車唔係話好多，<br />\n每日都係得10幾20分鐘西行入東隧係有龍。<br />\n西行條龍清左，東行基本上可以順住入，係有d仆街係隧道口前面cut黎cut去搞到慢"},{"pid":"d7d2ef522f78c38fb1c44b16f321c6b3b2d4cfcf","tid":467800,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"爛口耶人呀，一切都是神的安排，要感恩"},{"pid":"822a8aaf28e14350b0dc8da4105bd1e2656b7eb8","tid":467800,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實307行紅隧可能仲快</blockquote><br />\n以而家東隧狀況，307可能放工行番紅隧仲好，不過運吉傳統思維就係覺得東隧比紅隧順，所以多數唔批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b629a8d5afb7e9ed7adfeb38edb84fe3a9ac0b","tid":467800,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實307行紅隧可能仲快</blockquote><br />\n以而家東隧狀況，307可能放工行番紅隧仲好，不過運吉傳統思維就係覺得東隧比紅隧順，所以多數唔批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n東隧加大老山<br />\n紅隧+獅隧可能仲快，紅隧仲可以去遊艇會cut入去"},{"pid":"e347fab73718ba573da0bd3261de9052831c28e7","tid":467800,"uid":37717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我搭開307最塞反而係灣仔果段</blockquote><br />\n入境處果度都塞，但係短嘛<br />\n東隧果度由北角開始就停晒係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n塞撚完東隧仲要塞觀繞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n88R返沙田都行紅隧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1896a696b3580fcf573e584b7de92f4689197075","tid":467800,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我搭開307最塞反而係灣仔果段</blockquote><br />\n入境處果度都塞，但係短嘛<br />\n東隧果度由北角開始就停晒係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n塞撚完東隧仲要塞觀繞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n88R返沙田都行紅隧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n觀繞冇咁東隧口咁慢"}]}